  "body": "We send a `chainId` field as in the tx object that is the first param of `eth_sendTransaction`. It isn't part of the Ethereum JSON-RPC spec, and makes Buidler crash when using RSK.\r\n\r\nWe should probably do this and update `ethereumjs-tx` at the same time.",
